                <mrow>SA \amp = \int_{0}^{2\pi}\int_{0}^{5} r\sqrt{1+ \frac{4r^2\cos^2(t) +4r^2\sin^2(t) }{r^2\sin^2(t) +r^2\cos^2(t) }}\ dr\ d\theta</mrow>
                <mrow>\amp = \int_0^{2\pi}\int_0^5r\sqrt{5}\ dr\ d\theta</mrow>
                <mrow>\amp = 25\pi\sqrt{5}\approx 175.62</mrow>
              </md>
            </p>
          </solution>
        </webwork>
      </exercise>
